{
  "stem": "1704.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It would have been the same every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing ever happened, until I got typhoid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, if you call it laundry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just in the wash house where everybody washed themselves in cold water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we tried to keep very clean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody washing all, every morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, cold water and the toilets were in there too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were just overflowing sometimes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Since we were washing ourselves, we stood in the dirt, you might say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, for the old people's home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's terrible, but I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I know I did washing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how long, but then I went in the shoe commando.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You got a whole heap of old shoes and boots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had gotten a knife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything where it was stitched, undo the stitching.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you ended up with pieces of leather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what we had to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't tell us anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't ask.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the job we had to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Heaps, heaps.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now after the war, we realized, you know, they were from the people who were murdered.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't think so far ahead at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We also had, at one stage, they had-- they called them bread bags, little bags that probably where they-- if they went out to work, and I had to carry the lunch in.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And apparently, they were damaged with a bomb raid and waterlogged.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to sort them out, the good ones and the bad ones.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember some of the women made bras of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
